OL,3,CMore than 1,000 people waiting for
OL,4,Ctransplant in North East and Yorkshire
OL,6,FNew figures released today show that
OL,7,F1,046 people are currently on a
OL,8,Fwaiting list for an organ transplant
OL,9,Fin the North East and Yorkshire.
OL,11,FThey are part of a group of more than
OL,12,F8,000 people across the UK currently
OL,13,Fon the active transplant waiting list,
OL,14,Fthe highest number on record.
