OL,3,CMore than 1,000 people waiting for
OL,4,Ctransplant in North East and Yorkshire
OL,6,FDespite this, NHS Blood and Transplant
OL,7,Fsay the number of organ donors is
OL,8,Factually falling, in our region last
OL,9,Fyear there was a drop in deceased
OL,10,Forgan donors, with 166 people donating
OL,11,Fafter death, compared to 220 the
OL,12,Fprevious year.
OL,14,FThe number of transplant operations in
OL,15,Fthe North East and Yorkshire also fell
OL,16,Flast year, with 530 taking place,
OL,17,Fcompared with 560 in 2023.
