OL,3,CMore than 1,000 people waiting for
OL,4,Ctransplant in North East and Yorkshire
OL,6,FOne of those waiting for a transplant
OL,7,Fin the North East is 50-year-old Kerry
OL,8,FFear, who needs a heart transplant
OL,9,Fafter a lifetime of heart problems.
OL,11,FAt just nine weeks old, doctors
OL,12,Fdiscovered she only had three heart
OL,13,Fchambers, two holes in her heart and
OL,14,Fher two main arteries were the wrong
OL,15,Fway round.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/6
