OL,3,CMore than 1,000 people waiting for
OL,4,Ctransplant in North East and Yorkshire
OL,6,FAt the age of five, she had Fontan
OL,7,Fsurgery, a new procedure at the time,
OL,8,Fand since then she has had multiple
OL,9,Fopen heart surgeries and pacemakers
OL,10,Ffitted, but now a heart transplant is
OL,11,Fthe only option.
OL,13,FDespite living in Somerset, Kerry
OL,14,Fwould need to have her transplant at
OL,15,Fthe Freeman Hospital in Newcastle, as
OL,16,Fit is the only hospital in the country
OL,17,Fthat can carry out heart transplants
OL,18,Fon patients who have had Fontan
OL,19,Fsurgery.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/6
