OL,3,CMore than 1,000 people waiting for
OL,4,Ctransplant in North East and Yorkshire
OL,6,FShe said: "My transplant will
OL,7,Fhopefully make a massive difference, I
OL,8,Fhope to just be able to live and do
OL,9,Fmore physical activities than I have
OL,10,Fmy whole life.
OL,12,F"I've got to 50 and I can't run to the
OL,13,Fend of the road, my dream is to run a
OL,14,Fmarathon. I'd like to be able to go on
OL,15,Fa few more holidays and not worry. A
OL,16,Ftransplant would be confidence and
OL,17,Ffreedom."
