OL,3,CMore than 1,000 people waiting for
OL,4,Ctransplant in North East and Yorkshire
OL,6,FAnthony Clarkson from NHS Blood and
OL,7,FTransplant is urging people to take
OL,8,Faction by registering their decision
OL,9,Fon the NHS Organ Donation Register.
OL,11,FHe said: "We are facing an incredibly
OL,12,Fconcerning situation where more people
OL,13,Fthan ever are waiting for transplants,
OL,14,Fbut fewer donations are taking place.
OL,16,F"Tragically, someone will die today
OL,17,Fwaiting for a transplant and we
OL,18,Furgently need more people to register
OL,19,Ftheir decision to donate and to have
OL,20,Fthese vital conversations with their
OL,21,Ffamilies."
